thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Angie

author: Angie
title: Angie
text: Taxibox were nothing but a pleasure to deal with and made life so much simpler. Great value compared to a storage unit when you work out all the time, inconvenience and cost involved in moving everything into and out of one of those places! 100% would use them again and recommend to all our friends.
